description.summary:
Welcome to The Canopy in the thick of the forest. Here you will find it easy to relax and unwind. Leave the stresses and worries of everyday life behind and soak in the peaceful atmosphere of the woods. Enjoy watching nature through your panoramic window and star light window. The deck offers plenty of space and sun to enjoy and light up the bbq. Finish off your day with some s’mores on the fire then get cozy in bed next to the wood stove.

Minutes to three lakes and public beach.

